<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 2: WHY THIS AREA
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Elevated living with established character.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Carina Heights sits above the surrounding suburbs, offering views, larger blocks and a quiet elevated lifestyle that buyers find difficult to replicate closer to the CBD. It attracts a discerning buyer who values space and outlook.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I understand what makes Carina Heights properties stand out and how to communicate those qualities to the buyers most likely to act. That insight is the difference between a good result and a great one.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      The elevated position of Carina Heights puts it above the flat suburban grid, with many streets offering city views that buyers struggle to find at comparable price points closer in. Westfield Carindale is minutes away for everyday retail, and the South East Freeway provides quick CBD access that makes the suburb genuinely practical as well as scenic. The surrounding nature reserves along Whites Hill and Camp Hill give residents a green edge that buyers increasingly prioritise post-pandemic. Values here have firmed as buyers searching for the Camp Hill lifestyle at a more accessible entry point redirect attention to Carina Heights.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Carina Heights Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Inner-east Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Elevated Suburb</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Views and lifestyle</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/camp-hill" style="color:#c4912a;">Camp Hill</a>, <a href="/suburbs/carina" style="color:#c4912a;">Carina</a>, <a href="/suburbs/carindale" style="color:#c4912a;">Carindale</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

